WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Hello? (Hello, hello...) Is there anybody in there? Just nod if you can hear me.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Is there anyone home?

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Come on (come on, come on), now. I hear you're feeling down.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:33.000
Well I can ease the pain, and get you on your feet again.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Relax (relax, relax...). I'll need some information first.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Just the basic facts. Can you show me where it hurts?

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:55.000
There is no pain, you are receding.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:03.000
A distant ship smoke on the horizon.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:11.000
You are only coming through in waves.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Your lips move, but I can't hear what you're saying.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:25.000
When I was a child, I had a fever.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:34.000
My hands felt just like two balloons.
 